		</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
		
		<div class="comment-body"><p>When you&#8217;ve exhausted that, the PRI Au store has an audio PDC by Bill from 1983 which I believe is under $100, there&#8217;s the DVD set for $500 with both Geoff and Bill (which I agree with Jack, it is excellent) and there&#8217;s the actual Permaculture designer&#8217;s manual which I don&#8217;t recommend you read cover to cover but is a HUGE resource.  </p>
<p>After immersing yourself in the free information, grabbing one of the recorded PDC&#8217;s and being able to cross reference anything you have questions about in the PDM you&#8217;re pretty much there except for the certificate.  You can understand the system without the certificate and you can use it in your own life as long as you understand.</p>
<p>Besides, Jack and the TSP community are here to help with questions <img src="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" /> </p>
</div>

